'Nonoxynol-9', sometimes abbreviated as 'N-9', is an organic compound that is
used as a surfactant. It is a member of the nonoxynol family of nonionic
surfactants. N-9 and related compounds are ingredients in various cleaning and
cosmetic products. It is widely used in contraceptives for its spermicidal
properties. However, its use in STD prevention is controversial.
categories: Drugs acting on the genito-urinary system
